    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a functional driver at a lower price point. The engine and transmission are operational, though you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and a few non-essential electronic features that are currently non-functional. It is a reliable runner for daily commutes but will eventually benefit from some cosmetic and mechanical TLC.",
