    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures. I've taken great care of it, and it runs like a dream. If you're looking for a reliable ride that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features a precise double VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal power delivery to the rear wheels. Significant preventive maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection. The suspension geometry remains tight, offering the tactile feedback and lateral stability synonymous with the M-division's engineering. A driver-focused machine in solid condition.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
