    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-cared-for enthusiast car that balances performance with daily usability. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though closer inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's bolster. Every feature, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and premium audio system, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has a documented service history, including a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a reliable, honest vehicle that looks great in a driveway and performs even better on the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
